'''Kamonyi''' ni Akarere kari mu Ntara y'Amajyepfo, [[Rwanda]] . Umurwa mukuru wacyo ni Kamonyi, rimwe na rimwe izwi nka Gihinga.
[[Dosiye:KamonyiDist.png|thumb|Ikarita y'akarere ka Kamonyi]]

== Imirenge ==
Akarere ka Kamonyi kagabanijwemo [[Imirenge y’u Rwanda|imirenge]] 12 ( ''imirenge'' ): Gacurabwenge, Karama, Kayenzi, Kayumbu, Mugina, Musambira, Ngamba, Nyamiyaga, Nyarwaka, Rugalika, Rukoma na Runda.

